OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,FBert Hammond, Age 99, RAF
OL,8,FInterviewed 23 February 2024
OL,10,FAn air gunner on a Lancaster bomber
OL,11,Fwith a crew of seven, Mr Hammond's
OL,12,Faircraft spent the week leading up to
OL,13,FD-Day - and the night of D-Day -
OL,14,Fattacking enemy installations in
OL,15,FNorthern France.
OL,17,FBefore that he had been on bombing
OL,18,Fmissions to Germany and other parts of
OL,19,Foccupied Europe. The longest of these
OL,20,Fwas a nine-hour trip to Poland.
