OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,FHe said: "It got to one point I will
OL,7,Fbe honest, I didn't think I was going
OL,8,Fto make it. Because of the losses.
OL,9,FOther crews came in and left - never
OL,10,Fcame back.
OL,12,F"An air gunner of course is the eyes
OL,13,Fof the aircraft. The point is you
OL,14,Fsearch and search and search for enemy
OL,15,Fnight fighters because they were the
OL,16,Fbugbear of Bomber Command."
OL,18,FThe bombing targets began shifting to
OL,19,FFrance in the run-up to June 1944.
