OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,F"We were allocated around that period
OL,7,Ftargets to help the Army boys,'' Mr
OL,8,FHammond said.
OL,10,F"I did actually five operations in
OL,11,Feight days. These were all sorts of
OL,12,Ftargets to help the lads. Primarily
OL,13,Fthe defences of the Germans. Big
OL,14,Frailway junctions. Anything you could
OL,15,Fdo to cut off transport.
OL,17,F"The build up was some targets near
OL,18,FParis. Some further inland. But they
OL,19,Fweren't actually (Normandy).
OL,21,F"That came way closer to D-Day."
