OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,FHe remembers the day of the invasion
OL,7,Fclearly.
OL,9,F"We were being briefed in the briefing
OL,10,Froom. If your skipper is on the battle
OL,11,Forder you are on Ops that night. We
OL,12,Fwere being briefed for a target and
OL,13,Fsuddenly it was stopped. Cancelled for
OL,14,F24 hours. No one leaves the camp.
OL,16,F"The phone is cut off in the
OL,17,Fsergeants' mess and the officers'
OL,18,Fmess. It was the first we ever knew
OL,19,Fabout it.
