OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,F"Everybody was 'this is it. 'We are
OL,7,Ffinally going to get the chance to
OL,8,Ffree Europe'. No-one could stop
OL,9,Ftalking in the briefing room.
OL,11,F"We were doing day ops by then. We had
OL,12,Fnever done that before. We were not on
OL,13,Fduring the actual day of D-Day. We
OL,14,Fwent later that night. We didn't see
OL,15,Fthe fleet or anything. All you saw was
OL,16,Fa lot of gunfire.
OL,18,F"We were bombing selected targets to
OL,19,Fhelp the enemy lads. And then we just
OL,20,Fconcentrated on the invasion for a
OL,21,Fwhile."
