OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bert
OL,4,CHammond
OL,6,FMr Hammond's logbook from 1944 shows
OL,7,Ftargets that night included railway
OL,8,Fyards and a bridge.
OL,10,FBy war's end Mr Hammond had completed
OL,11,Fmore than 30 bombing missions and is
OL,12,Fthe only surviving member of his crew,
OL,13,Fwhich he likened to a band of brothers.
OL,15,FHe said: "Whatever we did we hope it
OL,16,Fhelped. The freedom we enjoy today is
OL,17,Fwhat you were looking for then. It's
OL,18,Fwhat we were fighting for."
